{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">=== <strong>Guardian Crystals</strong>  ===</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fairies are not strong enough to handle all the problems on their path without help. Use <strong>Guardian Crystals</strong> to borrow the abilities of your companions. You can choose a crystal with the desired effect for each enemy and switch them without limitations, but you will need to spend TP to support the crystal effect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465460/extras/store_help_crystalskill_english.png?t=1730779036\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you use <strong>Guardian Crystals</strong>, at special moments an ability with a star \u2605 will appear, allowing you to trigger <strong>Crystal Release</strong> \u2013 a powerful ability that will deal massive damage or buff your companions. <br>It can become the key to victory.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">=== <strong>Crafting items</strong> ===</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can gather materials for crafting. How? Explore levels, defeat enemies, or simply ask the fairies for them. Then, just create the items you need.<br>Improve your crafting skills, and you will be able to ease the effect of the Gimmicks. It\u2019s fun. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465460/extras/store_help_systhesis.png?t=1730779036\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">=== <strong>Gimmicks</strong> ===</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over time, <strong>Gimmicks</strong> will appear that will spice up the battles.<br>In other words, they will enhance the abilities of enemies or weaken yours.<br> It\u2019s up to you to decide which Gimmicks will have an effect, based on your equipment and skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2465460/extras/store_help_dungeon.png?t=1730779036\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">=== <strong>Powerful Enemies</strong> ===</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some enemies cannot be defeated head-on. <br>You will need to skillfully combine Gimmicks, your abilities, Guardian Crystals, and weapons to win. <br>Don\u2019t forget that you can create items with the help of the fairies.<br><br>\u203bThis game is a fan fiction of Touhou Project.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Adventure Again","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2465460/a158e21e55566c31943ee56bfe3b20d154103b96.jpg"},{"name":"First Strong Enemy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2465460/d9c65cec434381c2ef095df136fe73adfab654cf.jpg"},{"name":"Other World Exchange","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2465460/97a4ec2eb85ea8c405f33e0f715b72c34b06e83d.jpg"},{"name":"Omen","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2465460/1bbcf99ce3de3e602183826bfe2cbff197233e63.jpg"},{"name":"Sucker Punch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2465460/771b49ce875f0a8b5fbbf03993c4c156e693c01b.jpg"},{"name":"Special Move","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2465460/0dd1384c5399587d136774800008b54daff19fea.jpg"},{"name":"New Power","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2465460/aa5b1715695c2dfd78f5ce15d6917eb933fead0c.jpg"},{"name":"Safety Check","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2465460/f8d5fed16a4e88c9d9d7d15f830d3b81fa93dd8a.jpg"},{"name":"Fateful Battle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2465460/8a5a04b252f0b28d2f03903321cbe227eb12cedb.jpg"},{"name":"Lose Control","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcomm